# Github Actions for Automated Testing

This PR introduces GitHub workflows for testing Niffler Python Modules.

Two workflows are added for each of the following events

- Push to master or dev (.github/workflows/test.yml)
- Pull Request to dev (.github/workflows/test-pr.yml)

Currently, both workflows will execute Unit and Integration Tests using Github Actions.
